msgctxt "72_Tanimura"
msgid "Geez, what the hell are you guys doing? Don't you even worry about what people will think?"
msgstr "Cielos, ¿qué están haciendo? ¿Ni siquiera les importa lo que la gente pueda pensar?"

msgctxt "84_Drunk That Was Angry"
msgid "Ugh... Whatever happens, I can't let the guys at work hear about this one. Please, just take this and forget about it..."
msgstr "Ugh... pase lo que pase, no puedo dejar que los del trabajo sepan de esto. Por favor, toma esto y olvídate..."

msgctxt "168_Drunk That Was Angry"
msgid "Man, if my co-workers hear about this..."
msgstr "Amigo, si mis compañeros de trabajo supieran de esto..."

